### Example booking conflict flow
# This file is a placeholder for REST Client style API checks.
# Update endpoint paths after the backend booking API is implemented.

### Create approved booking
POST http://localhost:3000/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "equipmentId": "camera-01",
  "startsAt": "2026-07-06T10:00:00.000Z",
  "endsAt": "2026-07-06T12:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "approved"
}

### Attempt overlapping booking
POST http://localhost:3000/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "equipmentId": "camera-01",
  "startsAt": "2026-07-06T11:00:00.000Z",
  "endsAt": "2026-07-06T13:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "requested"
}
